jmark's Mail Handling Collection
================================

DISCLAIMER: (WiP) Use at your own risk! Major changes **highly** possible!

I know, there are major security and stability issues. But it work's quite
well, actually...

fetch.pl $INI
  : fetch and store mails from poop3 server to $INBOX

filter.pl $INBOX $ROOT $RULES
  : filter and shunt mails in $INBOX to $ROOT/<subdir> based on the rules in
    $RULES file

send.pl ...
  : wip.
